              background-color: #0a9830;
              color: #FFFFFF;
              text-align: center;
              font-size: 16px;
              padding: 12px 24px;
              transition: all 0.5s;
              cursor: pointer;
              box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 2, 0.3);"
